Klopp: &quot;There are so many stories from the past where very young boys showed up and later you didn&rsquo;t hear anything of them anymore.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It will not happen with Ben (Woodburn) but yes, he&rsquo;s in the best hands here at Liverpool.&quot;

Klopp on Woodburn: &ldquo;We know Ben best. He already did really good for us. It was a hard start to the pre-season.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on Woodburn: &quot;It was not too easy for him to perform as he already had. But the last two or three weeks he was really on a good way.&quot;

Klopp on Woodburn: &quot;Our target is that at the end we have him in the first team. Because we like him, we see his quality.&quot;<br />
<br />
